display property used to how your content show on your webpage.

display : inline 
display : inline-block 
display : block  
display : flex 
display : grid 
display : table 

some property are only used with display flex 
(1) flex (flex-grow, flex-shrink, flex-basis) (use in child class)
(2) flex-flow (flex-direction, flex-wrap)
(3) gap (row-gap, column-gap)
(4) justify-content 
(5) align-items 
(6) align-self (used in child class)

some property only used with display grid 
(1) grid-template-rows 
(2) grid-template-columns 
(3) grid-rows (grid-row-start, grid-row-end) (used in child class)
(5) grid-columns (grid-column-start, grid-column-end) (used in child class)
(6) gap (row-gap, column-gap)
(7) justify-items 
(8) align-content  
(9) align-self (used in child class)
(10) place-content 
